            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1115.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1115.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chicken thighs</strong> to the <strong>fajita seasoning</strong> and mix until they're fully coated in the spices</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
