    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid), with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chicken thighs</strong> and cook for 3-4 min on each side </p>\n<p>Meanwhile boil a kettle</p>",
